WHERE Gruppe == VARSIZED("Blutgase arteriell") AND Bez = VARSIZED("PTT") AND not (IsNaN(VarSizedToDouble(Wert))) AND VarSizedToDouble(Wert) > FLOAT64(90)
INTO File();
----
Detected high PTT(95 > 90 s) for patient 1007 at 15.01.2024 12:16(1705321000)

